{"tid":1031450,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"朋友遇到free Rider 點算好","createTime":"2019-02-21T15:52:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-21T15:55:28.000Z","uid":233180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f1294c2e11b6d2d90bda5deee86ce574343ee718","tid":1031450,"uid":233180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T15:52:59.000Z","msg":"朋友遇到free Rider( 我的朋友只求合格不求高分)<br />\n<br />\n仲有一個禮拜交功課但係到而家都冇人出過聲<br />\n<br />\n我同我朋友講千祈唔好益啲free Rider，我就畀咗個方案佢就係叫佢計下呢份project如果除開四份每個人要做幾多份量， 然後佢就淨係做其中一份。<br />\n<br />\n然後到present嗰日如果大家都係乜都冇做過 咁我就叫朋友同老師講 我嗰組其餘幾個人都係free rider所以我自己做咗自己嗰份， 我自己都可以present<br />\n<br />\n但係佢最後答我我唔係呢一種人，其實我都係好心唔想佢哋啲free rider撚， 但我估佢心入面嘅諗法係唔想打小報告篤背脊嗰啲諗法，但係我想講畀人踩到上心口自己都唔識反抗真係冇人可以幫到你。"},{"pid":"1c5616d9214a0322f714afc673b743575ffb994b","tid":1031450,"uid":233180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T15:55:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a2592fdd4d58cd530d30357ff6183d0b621ed80","tid":1031450,"uid":233180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T15:55:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}